{"tid":1078243,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"一氣呵成！的士連切兩線掉頭　網民：似賽車","createTime":"2019-03-26T07:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T08:38:13.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bdbd912b7137bb84b7289cf9f88afb8740fff315","tid":1078243,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"一氣呵成！的士連切兩線掉頭 網民：似賽車<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Cyiguz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Cyiguz&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=2fae671c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Cyiguz</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190326/photo/bkn-20190326142532647-0326_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190326145226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190326%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190326142532647-0326_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190326145226&h=8c53502c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現實版賽車遊戲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬路大晒U-turn技巧？近日觀塘有的士貪方便，竟恣意越線掉頭，全程需時更不到5秒！<br />\n<br />\n網友Wanwan Chu周一（25日）在Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」上載影片，顯示在常怡道近牛頭角上邨，有的士從九龍灣方向落橋後，忽然使出一招U形掉頭，越過雙白線及影線，往牛頭角方向駛去。<br />\n<br />\n有網民猜測的士：「入完氣，番定安街交更咁樣行係快啲嘅，不過都好快冇晒分啫！」，更批評的士：「條X頭真係當葡京彎咁過喎」、「依個位成日有人偷雞，其實左轉上去掉頭等多支燈，可能真係好難」。"},{"pid":"7305025f21b3f39eedb83da9fb16476f79f84ffe","tid":1078243,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"拉一拉手制"},{"pid":"6259b471c00e2a092c5b49d825abfe1ebdda9b65","tid":1078243,"uid":244558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"1823"}]}